# Kiwiwall (https://kiwiwall.com/)
# Good for: Surveys and offers with global reach
# Postback URL: https://your-domain.com/api/offers/callback?provider=Kiwiwall&status={status}&trans_id={trans_id}&sub_id={sub_id}&amount={amount}&offer_id={offer_id}&offer_name={offer_name}&signature={signature}&ip_address={ip_address}
